OL,3,CFrustration at 'nightmare' repairs on
OL,4,Croad where sewer has burst 16 times
OL,6,FResidents in Portsmouth have shared
OL,7,Ftheir frustration about the
OL,8,F"nightmare" disruption caused by
OL,9,Frepairs to a sewer underneath one of
OL,10,Fthe city's main streets.
OL,12,FEastern Road is closed in one
OL,13,Fdirection for a total of eight weeks
OL,14,Fso that Southern Water can carry out
OL,15,Fwhat it describes as "essential" works
OL,16,Fto a sewer line which has burst
OL,17,Fsixteen times over the last five years.
