OL,3,CFrustration at 'nightmare' repairs on
OL,4,Croad where sewer has burst 16 times
OL,6,FAlthough local people acknowledge the
OL,7,Fimportance of the works, there is
OL,8,Fconcerns over communication around the
OL,9,Fworks, and the knock-on effect that
OL,10,Fthey are having on traffic.
OL,12,FSouthern Water says that the repairs,
OL,13,Fwhich are costing #3.5 million, are
OL,14,Fcrucial to prevent widespread future
OL,15,Fdisruption from the sewers bursting
OL,16,Fagain.
OL,18,FThe company also stressed that it is
OL,19,Fusing technology to speed up the
OL,20,Fprocess as much as possible.
