OL,3,CFrustration at 'nightmare' repairs on
OL,4,Croad where sewer has burst 16 times
OL,6,FOne resident said: "I would say it's a
OL,7,Fnightmare, they didn't think enough
OL,8,Fabout it and the consequences.
OL,10,F"We all know Portsmouth is an island
OL,11,Fand when you shut one of the main
OL,12,Froads, as Eastern Road is, it's chaos
OL,13,Feverywhere."
OL,15,FAnother added: "I don't think there
OL,16,Fwas any planning to warn you as you're
OL,17,Fdriving in to say Eastern Road is very
OL,18,Fnarrow and we're doing work on it, and
OL,19,Fpeople are getting very upset with
OL,20,Feach other.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/8
