OL,3,CFrustration at 'nightmare' repairs on
OL,4,Croad where sewer has burst 16 times
OL,6,F"I realise Southern Water have got to
OL,7,Fdo water works which is what it's
OL,8,Fabout but one road closed in
OL,9,FPortsmouth leads to a lot of
OL,10,Ftailbacks."
OL,12,FGeorge Taylor, Director of Wastewater
OL,13,FOperations at Southern Water,
OL,14,Femphasised the importance of the
OL,15,Frepairs.
OL,17,FHe said: "The work we're doing here is
OL,18,Fto prevent any further disruption in
OL,19,Fthe future because we know that has
OL,20,Fbeen a thing over the last few years.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/8
