OL,6,F"We're well over halfway with the work
OL,7,Fthat we're doing.
OL,9,F"With work of this nature underground
OL,10,Fyou never know quite what you're going
OL,11,Fto come across but at the moment we're
OL,12,Fon track and we don't foresee any
OL,13,Fissues with that.
OL,15,F"Any changes with that (and) we will
OL,16,Fof course update people accordingly."
