OL,6,FThose working on the repairs explained
OL,7,Fthat they effectively involve making a
OL,8,Fpipe within a pipe in a way which is
OL,9,Fboth quicker and more environmentally
OL,10,Ffriendly.
OL,12,FPortsmouth North's Labour MP Amanda
OL,13,FMartin shared her constituents'
OL,14,Fconcerns regarding disruption caused
OL,15,Fby the works but said she's been
OL,16,Freassured after visiting the site.
