OL,3,CFrustration at 'nightmare' repairs on
OL,4,Croad where sewer has burst 16 times
OL,6,FShe said: "What I didn't know until
OL,7,Ftoday despite asking many questions is
OL,8,Fthat the Council have done things like
OL,9,Fremove other roadworks across the
OL,10,Fcity, change timing of traffic lights,
OL,11,Fthey have looked at "can we make it a
OL,12,Fdual road so we access both?"
OL,14,F"It would just be too dangerous
OL,15,Fbecause there's not enough to
OL,16,Fpartition and they would be worried
OL,17,Fabout head-on collisions so that's not
OL,18,Fan option.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/8
