OL,3,CFrustration at 'nightmare' repairs on
OL,4,Croad where sewer has burst 16 times
OL,6,F"But what I am also reassured about is
OL,7,Fthat works are on time and
OL,8,Feverything's running and it's really
OL,9,Finnovative and brilliant technology."
OL,11,FSouthern Water has thanked people for
OL,12,Ftheir patience and hope to have the
OL,13,Fworks finished by the end of February.
